nodes.text: J'Ruush was a male Whiphid, minion of Szajin the Hutt, serving as a commander of the InterStellar Regulators during the Galactic War. He was killed by an Imperial strike team.
J'Ruush is featured in the expansion Rise of the Hutt Cartel to the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic. He was the first Whipdid to appear in the series.
